    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/173bc2053ca6e16fccb94c38ac7e55d4.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=130 /></span>  <br>以错觉为基础的拼图挑战你的头脑。通过旋转镜头找到完美的角度来收拾残局并发现一个充满了神秘感的轻松故事。<br>   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/a07cf61948c935333a871f01d8753d25.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=80 /></span>  <br>没有什么是表面上所看到的！透过解答100个没有明显逻辑和结构的场景拼图来锐化你的感官。<br>      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/2cdcdd21c0c6553f672f41f12c192788.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=202 /></span>  <br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/90ce34057e348f445596df8ea592cc71.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=83 /></span>  <br>透过这个游戏在混乱的结构中侦测完美的角度。透过月来又艰难的挑战来测试你的视觉敏锐度。<br>        <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/5059d7d1a1c80026dab0ee2960147045.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=202 /></span>  <br>      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/500b166746693505de454df565017789.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=79 /></span>  <br>进入完美角度你会发现一个美丽的地方，在那里你拼出的每一个物品都将唤醒主角神秘的一生的相关回忆。<br>        <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/6863a046cbfb43e1a912e8b6573888e4.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=272 /></span>  <br>    <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/eaef65b367502ca30416a9a4f86f130a.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=80 /></span>  <br>在一个具有强烈吸引力的氛围中穿透沉浸主角的心灵。 <br>令人惊叹的画面、原创音乐和迷人的音效。<br>      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/c494b9bb5ee48ce1277bcc64bbc01436.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=356 /></span>  <br>      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/427780/extras/c104ed68c2fdebc8e89ea6a4764af529.avif?t=1510825841\" width=616 height=78 /></span>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过100个以视觉错觉为基础的拼图。<br></li><li>原创配乐。<br></li><li>由Guillermo Tato所创编。<br></li><li>自动将你的进度储存在云端。<br></li><li>翻译成11个语言版本：英语、西班牙语、法语、意大利语、德语、葡萄牙语、汉语、俄语、韩语、日语以及加泰罗尼亚语。<br></li><li>专业配音人员配音。<br></li><li>独一无二的画面和氛围。<br></li><li>操作简易且可以的轻松玩游戏。<br></li><li>36个成就和世界记录表。<br></li><li>外部控制器的完全支持。<br></li><li>使用于Windows、Mac和Linux操作系统的版本。</li></ul>",
